CHELICERAE. Ch basal article width 0.63, 2.7 times as long as wide at dorsal hump, with nearly straight dorsal margin in front of indentation and ventral margin (
Fig. 13G
). Distal article length 0.64, max width 0.23, movable finger length 0.27.

OVIPOSITOR. Ovipositor length 0.84, Rec sem of one tubular and 12 slightly elongated vesicles (
Fig. 11G
).
